Developer Terms of Use
des:
Hands-free voice control of your connected Westinghouse appliances. 

Ask Alexa to start, stop or change a setting, and it’s taken care of. 

You can use the appliance's name, shown in your +home or Alexa app, to say what you want to control.

This skill does not support all controls or appliances in the +home app. If you have any questions or comments, please contact +home customer support.

To get started, go to the Alexa app and enable the +home skill.

Supported devices:
Air conditioner
Dehumidifier

Contact us: voice@electrolux.com
